      <h1 class='title'>RAF Fairford</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c225WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_225ws' title='Col. 225WS &mdash; HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c225WS' name='column_225ws' href='#column_225ws' rel='bookmark'>225WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-05998'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_81'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-drew' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_81' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Drew' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-david-drew" title="Mr David Drew">Mr. Drew</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-05998">To ask the Secretary of State for Defence what the terms of agreement are between his Department and the US Air Force in the use of RAF Fairford. [88320]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-05999'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_82'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-adam-ingram' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_82' title='Link to this speech by Mr Adam Ingram' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-adam-ingram" title="Mr Adam Ingram">Mr. Ingram</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-05999">The presence of the United States Air Force at RAF Fairford is, as with all bases made available to United States visiting forces in the United Kingdom, governed by the NATO Status of Forces Agreement 1951 and additional confidential arrangements.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
